### Register User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "dd",
  "email": "abc@gmail.com",
  "password": "a",
  "phoneNo":"3274832749"
}

### Login User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "abc@gmail.com",
  "password": "a"
}

