### Create Product

POST http://localhost:5000/api/products/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Product2",
  "description": "This is product 1",
  "price":100,
  "category":"electronics",
  "stock":10
}

### Get All Products

GET http://localhost:5000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

